rsync_baler [-h] [-v] [-V] [-f] [-x] [-R] [-b] [-j FILE] [-s sta_regex] [-r sta_regex] [-p pf] [-m email,email]

=head1 ARGUMENTS

Recognized flags:

=over 2

=item B<-h> 

Help. Produce this documentation

=item B<-v> 

Produce verbose output while running

=item B<-V>

Produce very-verbose output (debuggin)

