=item B<-p file>

Parameter file name to use.

=item B<-j FILE>

Produce report of databases in json format and dump the data in FILE. Avoid running
in archival mode.

=item B<-s regex>

Select station regex. ('STA1|STA2' or 'A...|B.*')

=item B<-r regex>

Reject station regex. ('STA1|STA2' or 'A...|B.*')

